text: Alfred Schwarzenbach (born 8 October 1941) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
